# Parmesan Minestrone

Based on [Chrissy Teigen Cravings Hungry for More](https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/553580/cravings-hungry-for-more-by-chrissy-teigen-with-adeena-sussman) ([archive](http://web.archive.org/web/20250616010240/https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/553580/cravings-hungry-for-more-by-chrissy-teigen-with-adeena-sussman/)), pg. 50

